{"tid":2444120,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"美聯測量：黃竹坑站第六期入意向書反應熱烈 估值近百億元","createTime":"2021-03-12T13:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T18:29:39.000Z","uid":166360,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cc3cfbc9871e802f82c7bbe36edf0603b22285c1","tid":2444120,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T13:24:43.000Z","msg":"美聯測量：黃竹坑站第六期入意向書反應熱烈 估值近百億元<br />\n19:10 2021/03/12<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......美聯測量師行董事林子彬表示，是次推出的第六期為黃竹坑站最後一期的發展項目，而且位處鐵路站上蓋及接近商場，加上市區及鐵路站上蓋項目未來供應極為罕有，故是次項目繼續吸引大批發展商遞交參與項目的「入場券」。最終入標數目將視乎招標條款而定，若連同補地價及分紅等，樓面地價估值達每呎1.7萬至1.9萬元計算，總值約85.6億至95.7億元水平......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2900064/%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E6%B8%AC%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%9A%E9%BB%83%E7%AB%B9%E5%9D%91%E7%AB%99%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AD%E6%9C%9F%E5%85%A5%E6%84%8F%E5%90%91%E6%9B%B8%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%E7%86%B1%E7%83%88%20%E4%BC%B0%E5%80%BC%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E5%84%84%E5%85%83?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2900064%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E9%2587%258F%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25BB%2583%25E7%25AB%25B9%25E5%259D%2591%25E7%25AB%2599%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2583%2588%2520%25E4%25BC%25B0%25E5%2580%25BC%25E8%25BF%2591%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXIwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=9f9f3104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2900064/%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E6%B8%AC%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%9A%E9%BB%83%E7%AB%B9%E5%9D%91%E7%AB%99%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AD%E6%9C%9F%E5%85%A5%E6%84%8F%E5%90%91%E6%9B%B8%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%E7%86%B1%E7%83%88%20%E4%BC%B0%E5%80%BC%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E5%84%84%E5%85%83?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">將來賣到呎價30k無難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"}